anuelle/Kamo Tsuba Shrine|qq=}}, [[:en:Nagata Shrine|Nagata Shrine]], etc. | related_clans = {{ill|Miwa clan|ja|三輪氏|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Miwa clan|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 大神氏}}, {{ill|Kamo no Asomi clan|ja|賀茂氏|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamo no Asomi clan|qq=}}, {{ill|Munakata clan|ja|宗像氏|1=Munakata clan|fr|Clan Munakata|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Munakata clan|13=User:Immanuelle/Munakata clan|qq=}}, {{ill|Nagakuni no Miyatsuko|ja|長国造|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nagakuni no Miyatsuko|qq=}}, {{ill|Tosa no Miyatsuko|ja|都佐国造|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tosa no Miyatsuko|qq=}}, {{ill|Hata clan|ja|波多国造|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hata clan|qq=}}, {{ill|Ishibe clan|ja|石辺氏|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishibe clan|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} }}
